    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years. I've taken great care of it, and it still runs like a dream. It's the perfect fit for anyone looking for a dependable car that's ready for many more adventures. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love how it handles as much as I have!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
