    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a high-revving example of the E46 platform, powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this vehicle has been maintained with an enthusiast's eye; the VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, providing the telepathic steering feedback these cars are known for. While it shows the honest patina of a well-loved driver, the compression is strong across all cylinders, and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline without hesitation.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
