    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy finish, showing only minor, superficial signs of road use that are consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin remains a pristine environment; the seating surfaces are supple and free of significant wear, while the original carpeting has been protected by all-weather mats. Every feature, including the premium sound system, navigation, and heated seats, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule with recent fluid changes and a fresh set of tires. It drives straight and true, with a quiet cabin and a responsive engine that delivers power smoothly. This is a smoke-free, garage-kept car that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any hidden needs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
